'''Rick Leonardi''' (born [[August 9]], [[1950s|1957]]) is an [[Wikipedia:Americans|American]] [[Star Wars comic books|comic book]] artist who pencilled several ''[[Star Wars]]'' titles for [[Dark Horse Comics]], including the four-issue [[Star Wars: General Grievous|''General Grievous'']] series and [[W. Haden Blackman|Haden Blackman's]] [[Star Wars: Darth Vader and the Lost Command|''Darth Vader and the Lost Command'']].

